thread.title: BRIEF-Federal Bank Dec-Qtr Profit Up About 26 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Federal Bank Dec-Qtr Profit Up About 26 pct
text:
Jan 15 (Reuters) - Federal Bank Ltd:
* DEC QUARTER NET PROFIT 2.60 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS NET PROFIT OF 2.06 BILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO
* CONSENSUS FORECAST FOR DEC QUARTER NET PROFIT WAS 2.63 BILLION RUPEES
* DEC QUARTER INTEREST EARNED 25.01 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 22.81 BILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO
* DEC QUARTER PROVISIONS 1.62 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 1.59 BILLION RUPEES YEAR AGO
* DEC QUARTER GROSS NPA 2.52 PERCENT VERSUS 2.39 PERCENT PREVIOUS QUARTER
* DEC QUARTER NET NPA 1.36 PERCENT VERSUS 1.32 PERCENT PREVIOUS QUARTER Source text: bit.ly/2B0fnyR Further company coverage:
